item.title: The Sims 3 Has Been Leaked!
item.dc:creator: NavMan
item.description:
My god, the freewill AI is horrible. I was playing as a single dude who impregnated a girlfriend who lived in another house. A few days after the birth, I went over to the chicks house to see how the baby was doing, and she just leaves her lying on the floor! She only fulfils the very basic needs of the baby like changing diapers and feeding it. other than that, the kid is on the floor all night, while the mum is at work etc. Criminal negligence!

item.title: The Sims 3 Has Been Leaked!
item.dc:creator: Level
item.description:
NavMan:

One real shortcoming in Sims 2 was that if a child made a friend when he was young, as he grew up the friend would stay young (if he lived in another house that is). Made for interesting situations such as an 80 year old man having a 13 year old as a best friend lol. Has this been fixed in Sims 3?

The problem with this is that you don’t want a family to live their life while you’re not controlling them. It’d be super hard to fix. I haven’t gotten one of my sims to age yet, so we’ll see.
